title: Moin Market Capitalization Tops $641,503.00 (MOIN)
content: Moin (CURRENCY:MOIN) traded 3.6% higher  against the dollar during the one day period ending at 17:00 PM Eastern on May 18th. Over the last seven days, Moin has traded 6.2% higher  against the dollar. Moin has a total market cap of $641,503.00 and $1,702.00 worth of Moin was traded on exchanges in the last 24 hours. One Moin coin can now be purchased for about $0.0840 or 0.00001101 BTC on popular exchanges including Cryptopia,  C-CEX,  Livecoin and  CoinExchange.    Here is how related cryptocurrencies have performed over the last 24 hours:    Get Moin alerts:     Crave (CRAVE) traded down 3.3% against the dollar and now trades at $0.21 or 0.00002795 BTC.  Bitswift (SWIFT) traded up 3.1% against the dollar and now trades at $0.58 or 0.00007658 BTC.  TeslaCoin (TES) traded 4.2% higher  against the dollar and now trades at $0.0285 or 0.00000374 BTC.  ShadowCash (SDC) traded 25% higher  against the dollar and now trades at $0.0953 or 0.00001249 BTC.  Bitstar (BITS) traded up 2.8% against the dollar and now trades at $0.0103 or 0.00000135 BTC.  Ratecoin (XRA) traded 5.2% lower  against the dollar and now trades at $0.0015 or 0.00000019 BTC.  Swing (SWING) traded up 2.4% against the dollar and now trades at $0.0534 or 0.00000699 BTC.  WINCOIN (WC) traded 0.5% higher  against the dollar and now trades at $0.32 or 0.00004157 BTC.  ClubCoin (CLUB) traded 1.6% lower  against the dollar and now trades at $0.36 or 0.00004722 BTC.  Hyper (HYPER) traded up 9.1% against the dollar and now trades at $0.0188 or 0.00000246 BTC.   About Moin      Moin is a PoW/PoS coin that uses the  Proof of Stake hashing algorithm. It was first traded on October 9th, 2015. Moin’s total supply is 7,635,428 coins. Moin’s official Twitter account is @MoinCrypto and its Facebook page is accessible here . The Reddit community for Moin is /r/Moin and the currency’s Github account can be viewed here . Moin’s official website is discovermoin.com .    According to CryptoCompare, “0-19: 0 MOIN20-999: 79 MOIN1000-17999: 59 MOIN18000-19999: 89 MOIN 18000-19999: POS “    Moin Coin Trading    Moin can be purchased on these cryptocurrency exchanges: Cryptopia,  Livecoin,  C-CEX and  CoinExchange.  It is usually not possible to purchase alternative cryptocurrencies such as Moin directly using US dollars. Investors seeking to acquire Moin should first purchase Ethereum or Bitcoin using an exchange that deals in US dollars such as Gemini, Coinbase or Changelly. Investors can then use their newly-acquired Ethereum or Bitcoin to purchase Moin using one of the aforementioned exchanges.
